title: American Horror Story Weekly Wednesday Live Stream
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I keep missing the streams sorry Mary. But I love your shirt love the colors. Also can't wait for your fun videos leading up to the premier of the new season. Still my favorite AHS YouTube channel! ❤️ Gotta question for you... Would you like to see a theme about a Prison, Area 51 or a Hospital theme possibly taking place during the TB outbreak?
I saw a theory online where Emma Roberts character this season is Chanel Oberlin from Scream Queens who dyed her hair brunette and is an actress on the movie set for a 1984 movie!

These “teasers” aren’t actual teasers for the season, it’s for the sweepstakes, it’s going to be slasher though no one can convince me otherwise, I mean I’m assuming that it’s for both? referring that the killer will lurk
